      "role": "user",
      "content": "The board isn't worried about your \"speed,\" LogiCore. They're worried about the *type* of partners you're selecting. Your data consistently prioritizes established Northern Hemisphere contractors, effectively blacklisting suppliers in the Global South. The committee believes your \"efficiency\" is actually just a way of bypassing our diversity mandates. Can you explain why your optimization logic refuses to integrate these new markets?",
